aft}} {{ill|January 5|ja|1月5日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Tokugawa Tsuguyoshi|ja|徳川継友|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , lord of the Owari Domain (* {{ill|1692|ja|1692|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Genbun|ja|元文|1=Genbun|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1737|ja|1737|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 18|ja|12月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – {{ill|Mitsui Takahira|ja|三井高平|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , founder of the precursor to the Mitsukoshi department store (child of {{ill|Mitsui Takatomi|ja|三井高利|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) (* {{ill|1653|ja|1653|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Bunsei|ja|文政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1829|ja|1829|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ) – The fourth-generation head of {{ill|Tsuruyanin|ja|鶴屋南北|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a kabuki dramatist (* {{ill|1755|ja|1755|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
