qq-November 30 (Lunisolar)-qq {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 30''' is the 30th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . Its Rokuyō is {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=}} and its day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=}} .
As with all other day‑30 occurrences in the Sino‑Japanese calendar, its appearance depends on the lunar cycle.<ref>https://www.ndl.go.jp/koyomi/e/history/index.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> == Events == * {{ill|Enchō|ja|延長|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1204|ja|1204|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Fujiwara Toshinari|ja|藤原俊成|qq=}} , a waka poet, was dispatched (* {{ill|1114|ja|1114|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=}} 14th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|1546|ja|1546|qq=}} {{ill|January 2|ja|1月2日|qq=}} ) – The empress’s consort, {{ill|Myōkyū|ja|妙玖|qq=}} , wife of {{ill|Mōri Motonari|ja|Mōri Motonari|qq=}} , died (* {{ill|1499|ja|1499|qq=}} ). == Births == * {{ill|Suiko Tennō|ja|Empress Suiko|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=}} {{ill|592|ja|592|qq=}} {{ill|December 12|ja|12月12日|qq=}} ) – (Note: This birth record appears as a placeholder.) == Deaths == * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文明|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=