rian calendar]] {{ill|1737|ja|1737|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1737|qq=}} [[:en:December 18|December 18]] ) – {{ill|Mitsui Takahira|ja|三井高平|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mitsui Takahira|qq=}} , founder of the precursor to the Mitsukoshi department store (child of [[:en:Mitsui Takatoshi|Mitsui Takatomi]] ) (* {{ill|1653|ja|1653|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1653|qq=}} ). * [[:en:Bunsei|Bunsei]] 12th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] {{ill|1829|ja|1829|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1829|qq=}} [[:en:December 22|December 22]] ) – The fourth-generation head of {{ill|Tsuruyanin|ja|鶴屋南北|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuruyanin|qq=}} , a kabuki dramatist (* {{ill|1755|ja|1755|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1755|qq=}} ).
